## 8. Deploy
- Target: backend API + web SPA on same host
- Trigger: push `main` (auto) or `workflow_dispatch` via `.github/workflows/deploy.yml`
- Auto-deploy paths: `backend/**`, `web/**`, `scripts/deploy.sh`, `.cpanel.yml`, `.github/workflows/deploy.yml`
- Prereq: `npm run build:prod` + commit `web/dist/`
- Secrets: `CPANEL_USER`, `CPANEL_TOKEN`
- Flow: Actions `VersionControl/update` -> `VersionControlDeployment/create` -> cPanel runs `.cpanel.yml` -> `scripts/deploy.sh`
- Verify: Actions green, `GET /api/v1/ping` ok, SPA served on production URL
- Source of truth: `.github/workflows/deploy.yml`, `.github/workflows/web-ci.yml`, `.cpanel.yml`, `scripts/deploy.sh`, `backend/DEPLOY.md`